      open the terminal

step1 : install the streamlit
        pip install streamlit
step2 : After installation of streamlit we have to create a virtual environlmenment to run the streamlit in python
        python -m venv myenv
step3 : after creating virtual environment open the path where lightning sensor is put up & activate another virtual environment, 
        the lightning code is uploaded inside lightning floder
        source /home/lightning/venv/bin/activate
step4 : open the Documents inside virtual environment platform
        cd Documents
step5 : read alln files inside documents
        ls
step6 : run the code
        steamlit run python_lightning_sonsor.py

        it is open new window show the lightning sensor output..
